<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />He blessed his soul while he lived—</para>

<para style="q1">and men praise you when you live for yourself—</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />he will go to the generation of his fathers</para>

<para style="q1">and they will never see the light again.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />One who has wealth but no understanding</para>

<para style="q1">is like the beasts, which perish.</para>
